{"tid":1451970,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"愈嚟愈多武警扮警察係好事嚟 文宣入","createTime":"2019-08-11T22:42:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-27T02:53:26.000Z","uid":144262,"like":54,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"956e85463020189442925780e6d815e3cbbee3ad","tid":1451970,"uid":144262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T22:42:33.000Z","msg":"所謂將計就計 依家愈來愈多武警混入防暴入面打鳩啲手足<br />\n<br />\n相信大家都好撚嬲<br />\n<br />\n如果繼續係咁遲早有手足出事<br />\n<br />\n跟據依家情況可以推斷之後係更加唔樂觀<br />\n<br />\n所以希望文宣組可以大力咁將<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">香港警察已被武警替代</span>傳開去<br />\n<br />\n咁有乜用？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">係好有用！依家示威者唔可以隨意升級武力係因<br />\n<br />\n為怕失民意  係其他市民心目中佢地仲係香港人</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">如果文宣成功將呢個觀念spread開</span><br />\n<br />\n警隊將會同市民疏遠<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">前線手足就有<span style=\"color: red;\">合理理由升級武力</span>而唔係捱打冇得還手</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">甚至有機會玩玉林狗肉節</span><br />\n<br />\n我唔想再見到有手足受傷喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1b4eb124f238ebf61730c47adc763081d02b762","tid":1451970,"uid":144262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T22:43:35.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cab2cc5e33934551b39e7ef0cd9b59ff57490c99","tid":1451970,"uid":144262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T22:45:09.000Z","msg":"幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27e63989661524fc058cebc62c4ce37d2dd6efde","tid":1451970,"uid":35457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T22:46:59.000Z","msg":"TVB 最新深夜版本<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/aJ3pKRC1zqY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FaJ3pKRC1zqY&d=926QiOG7cNu1sWdYPFF%2FaIoeW3mBCvqo%2FKk1k%2BmNMw8%3D&h=c9496bcd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/aJ3pKRC1